April 14 (Reuters) - The following financial services industry appointments were announced on Monday. To inform us of other job changes, email to moves@thomsonreuters.com.  LPL FINANCIAL HOLDINGS INC The company said its unit LPL Financial appointed William Morrissey as managing director of its Independent Advisor Services business. Morrissey will lead the unit, which provides solutions and relationship management to the company's independent advisors.

